%3Cli%3EThe%20token%20jumped%2011.7%25%20to%20a%20new%20high%20for%20the%20year%2C%20reaching%20above%20%2447%2C500.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThat's%20as%20spot%20ETF%20flows%20have%20significantly%20slowed%2C%20and%20should%20no%20longer%20be%20a%20headwind.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20failing%20to%20meet%20market%20hopes%20in%20January%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcurrencies%2Fbtc-usd%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%26utm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%3Ebitcoin%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20surged%20sharply%20to%20its%20highest%20level%20in%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20token%20gained%2011.7%25%20through%20the%20week%2C%20reaching%20a%20price%20of%20around%20%2447%2C565.%20This%20change%20of%20fortune%20keeps%20the%20%24100%2C000%20price%20target%20achievable%20by%20the%20year's%20end%2C%20Standard%20Chartered's%20Geoff%20Kendrick%20wrote%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Head%20of%20FX%20Research%20has%20long%20held%20bullish%20expectations%20for%20the%20cryptocurrency%20and%20anticipates%20that%20the%20price%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-outlook-200000-2025-inflows-spot-etf-approval-sec-2024-1%5C%22%3Ereach%20%24200%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20end-2025.%20Part%20of%20his%20forecast%20is%20built%20on%20optimism%20around%20the%20fresh%20bitcoin%20spot%20ETFs%2C%20which%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2Fnews%2Fstatement%2Fgensler-statement-spot-bitcoin-011023%5C%22%3Eapproved%20by%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20January%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Kendrick%20argued%20that%20these%20new%20investment%20vehicles%20should%20drive%20massive%20inflows%20into%20the%20crypto%20sector%2C%20providing%20an%20outlet%20for%20more%20traditional%20financial%20players%20to%20join%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20bitcoin%20slumped%20heavily%20after%20the%20spot%20ETFs%20hit%20the%20market%2C%20and%20the%20cryptocurrency's%20price%20bottomed%20at%20around%20%2439%2C450%20by%20January's%20end.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20have%20cited%20the%20Grayscale%20ETF's%20heavy%20outflows%20as%20a%20factor%20for%20bitcoin's%20mixed%20performance.%20The%20investment%20vehicle%20was%20converted%20from%20a%20pre-existing%20bitcoin%20trust%20fund%2C%20which%20meant%20it%20already%20held%20billions%20worth%20of%20bitcoin%20before%20having%20to%20compete%20with%2010%20other%20ETFs.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20surge%20of%20outflows%2C%20with%20the%20GBTC%20fund%20losing%20%242.5%20billion%20in%20its%20worst%20week%2C%20a%20JPMorgan%20note%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221262%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Comparison%20of%20bitcoin%20spot%20ETF%20flows%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c684a043bb77284ba59be2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22996%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20Flows%20and%20Liquidity%2C%20February%207%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20has%20significantly%20slowed%2C%20which%20could%20be%20a%20possible%20reason%20bitcoin%20has%20shot%20back%20up%2C%20Kendrick%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20is%20simply%20down%20to%20the%20changing%20flow%20dynamics%20in%20the%20new%20US%20ETFs.%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20a%20Friday%20email%2C%20reacting%20to%20bitcoin's%20upside.%20He%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BGBTC%20selling%20seems%20to%20have%20slowed%20(to%20an%20average%20of%20USD59mn%20a%20day%20this%20week)%20while%20flows%20into%20the%20other%20ETFs%20continue%20to%20be%20strong%20(average%20USD244mn%20a%20day%20this%20week).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20enough%20to%20achieve%20the%20conditions%20needed%20for%20Kendrick's%20year-end%20price%20forecast.%20Previously%2C%20he%20outlined%20that%20between%20437%2C000%20and%201.32%20million%20new%20bitcoins%20should%20eventually%20be%20held%20by%20spot%20ETFs%2C%20which%20could%20make%20a%20%24200%2C000%20price%20point%20possible.%20As%20outflows%20stop%20completely%2C%20net%20inflows%20should%20be%20able%20to%20reach%20%2450%20billion%20to%20%24100%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-price-rally-cryptocurrency-spot-etfs-forecast-inflows-standard-chartered-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707509874000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654a98d4b788914e5551f6a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-rally-cryptocurrency-spot-etfs-forecast-inflows-standard-chartered-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bitcoin%20spot%20ETF%20flows%20should%20no%20longer%20be%20a%20headwind%2C%20and%20bitcoin%20could%20continue%20rallying%20this%20year%2C%20Standard%20Chartered%20said%20in%20an%20email.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22fdemott%40insider.com%20(Filip%20De%20Mott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A100%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-rally-cryptocurrency-spot-etfs-forecast-inflows-standard-chartered-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Babil%20Khan%20misses%20late%20father%20Irrfan%20Khan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707509102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107567195%2Cimgsize-109086.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbabil-khan-misses-late-father-irrfan-khan-heartfelt-post%2Farticleshow%2F107567202.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107567202.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBabil%20Khan%20shares%20his%20deep%20emotions%20and%20memories%20of%20his%20father%20Irrfan%20Khan.%20He%20expresses%20his%20desire%20for%20one%20last%20dance%20with%20his%20father%20and%20his%20gratitude%20for%20the%20lessons%20he%20learned.%20Babil%20is%20determined%20to%20find%20his%20father's%20presence%20again.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbabil-khan-misses-late-father-irrfan-khan-heartfelt-post%2Farticleshow%2F107567202.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zyn%20confirms%20that%20business%20is%20booming%20in%20the%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Containers%20of%20%26quot%3BZyn%26quot%3B%20nicotine%20pouches.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b822997a3d27148875a035%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EContainers%20of%20Zyn%20nicotine%20pouches.%3Cp%3EMichael%20M.%20Santiago%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EZyn%20has%20been%20making%20the%20rounds%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20it%20shows%20%E2%80%94%20business%20was%20booming%20in%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShipments%20of%20the%20nicotine%20pouches%20were%20up%2062%25%20year-over-year%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMedical%20experts%20warn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ftreatments%2Fvaping-vs-smoking%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enicotine%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20be%20addictive%20and%20have%20harmful%20effects.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EZyn%20saw%20massive%20growth%20in%20the%20US%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20385%20million%20cans%20of%20the%20flavored%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeople-are-putting-nicotine-pouches-in-their-butthole-penis-foreskins-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enicotine%20pouches%3C%2Fa%3E%20shipped%20in%20the%20US%20in%202023%2C%20up%2062%25%20year-over-year%2C%20according%20to%20an%20earnings%20report%20released%20Thursday%20by%20Philip%20Morris%20International%2C%20which%20owns%20Zyn's%20manufacturer%2C%20Swedish%20Match.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20expects%20to%20do%20even%20better%20business%20this%20year%2C%20forecasting%20US%20shipment%20of%20roughly%20520%20million%20cans%20of%20the%20pouches%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20shipments%20to%20retailers%20and%20distributors%20can%20outpace%20actual%20consumer%20sales%20of%20the%20pouches%2C%20those%20year-over-year%20growth%20numbers%20indicate%20that%20Zyn%20sales%20are%20booming%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchuck-schumer-nicotine-zyn-republican-right-wing-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZyn%20has%20found%20favor%20with%20political%20conservatives%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20GOP%20lawmakers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-streets-underground-drug-abuse-culture-cocaine-adderall-zyn-mushrooms-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWall%20Street%20traders%20who%20say%20they%20use%20it%20for%20focus%20and%20energy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20also%20been%20having%20a%20moment%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20so-called%20%26quot%3BZynfluencers%26quot%3B%20lauding%20it%20on%20platforms%20like%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMedical%20experts%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fntr%2Farticle%2F23%2F9%2F1590%2F6285126%3Flogin%3Dfalse%23255584865%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4363846%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudies%3C%2Fa%3E%20warn%20nicotine%20can%20be%20addictive%20and%20can%20have%20harmful%20effects%20on%20the%20body%2C%20including%20its%20cardiovascular%20and%20respiratory%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Philip%20Morris%20International%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20best%20thing%20anyone%20worried%20about%20their%20health%20can%20do%20is%20to%20quit%2C%20or%20never%20start%2C%20using%20nicotine.%20For%20those%20that%20don't%20quit%2C%20what%20matters%20most%20is%20helping%20them%20switch%20to%20better%20alternatives.This%20is%20the%20comparator%20that%20matters%20most.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BZYN%20is%20marketed%20exclusively%20to%20current%20adult%20nicotine%20consumers%20as%20an%20alternative%20%E2%80%94%20with%20cigarettes%20being%20the%20most%20harmful%20nicotine%20product%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Senate%20Majority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%20called%20on%20federal%20agencies%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20Zyn%20and%20investigate%20its%20marketing%20practices%2C%20particularly%20as%20they%20relate%20to%20young%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PMI%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20limit%20marketing%20to%20those%20who%20are%20of%20legal%20age%20of%20purchase%20(aged%2021%20and%20above)%20who%20would%20otherwise%20continue%20to%20smoke%20or%20use%20nicotine%20products.%20We%20follow%20the%20law%20and%20voluntarily%20do%20more%20than%20regulations%20require.%20For%20example%2C%20we%20age-gate%20our%20digital%20channels%20to%2021-plus%20and%20we%20do%20not%20use%20social%20media%20influencers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20law%20that%20took%20effect%20in%202022%20forbids%20sellers%20and%20manufacturers%20of%20non-tobacco%20nicotine%20from%20selling%20to%20people%20under%2021%3B%20marketing%20the%20items%20as%20modified%20risk%20tobacco%20products%20without%20FDA%20authorization%3B%20and%20distributing%20free%20samples.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20use%20Zyn%20while%20working%3F%20We'd%20like%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Asjackson%40insid