2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-hamas-war-netanyahu-orders-evacuation-of-rafah-as-aid-agencies-warn-escalation-in-refugee-city-will-be-devastating-13067630%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-hamas-war-netanyahu-orders-evacuation-of-rafah-as-aid-agencies-warn-escalation-in-refugee-city-will-be-devastating-13067630%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reliance%20Consumer%20to%20acquire%20Ravalgaon%20Sugar%20confectionery%20brands%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707499923000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2020-01%2F23%2Ffull%2F1579781679-7472.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-consumer-to-acquire-ravalgaon-sugar-confectionery-brands-124020901761_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22RCPL%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20Reliance%20Retail%20Ventures%20Ltd%20(RRVL)%2C%20which%20is%20the%20retail%20arm%20of%20Mukesh%20Ambani-led%20Reliance%20Industries%20Ltd%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-consumer-to-acquire-ravalgaon-sugar-confectionery-brands-124020901761_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-consumer-to-acquire-ravalgaon-sugar-confectionery-brands-124020901761_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-consumer-to-acquire-ravalgaon-sugar-confectionery-brands-124020901761_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Election%20Manifesto'%20Says%20Opposition%20As%20Lok%20Sabha%20Discusses%20Centre's%20White%20Paper%20on%20Economy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F24160818%2FScreenshot-2023-03-24-at-4.07.15-PM_cleanup.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Friday%20(February%209)%20discussed%20the%20centre%E2%80%99s%20white%20paper%20on%20the%20Indian%20economy%2C%20with%20opposition%20members%20criticising%20the%20move%20to%20bring%20a%20document%20detailing%20the%20ten%20years%20of%20the%20UPA%20government%20(2004-2014)%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Celection%20manifesto%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20attempt%E2%80%9D%20to%20defame%20the%20previous%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discussion%20which%20continued%20for%20about%20seven%20hours%20ended%20with%20the%20house%20defeating%20by%20a%20voice%20vote%2C%20the%20motions%20moved%20by%20opposition%20members%20RSP%20MP%20N.K.%20Premchandran%20and%20TMC%20MP%20Saugata%20Roy%20disapproving%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETitled%20%E2%80%98White%20Paper%20on%20the%20Indian%20Economy%E2%80%99%2C%20the%2059-page%20document%20that%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcentre-tables-white-paper-on-10-years-of-upa-hours-after-congresss-black-paper-on-modi-govts-failures%5C%22%3Epresented%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20Lower%20House%20on%20Thursday%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20Congress%20released%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-releases-black-paper-on-modi-governments-failures%5C%22%3Eblack%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20failures%2C%20says%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20inherited%20an%20economy%20that%20was%20%E2%80%9Cin%20a%20fragile%20state%3B%20public%20finances%20were%20in%20bad%20shape%3B%20there%20was%20economic%20mismanagement%20and%20financial%20indiscipline%3B%20and%20there%20was%20widespread%20corruption.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20reply%20to%20the%20Lower%20House%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20discussion%2C%20union%20minister%20of%20finance%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20responding%20to%20arguments%20by%20opposition%20MPs%20who%20called%20the%20document%20%E2%80%9Cbaseless%E2%80%9D%20said%20that%20the%20paper%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cserious%20document%E2%80%9D%20based%20on%20%E2%80%9Cevidence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuoting%20prime%20minister%20Modi%20in%202016%2C%20Sitharaman%20said%20that%20it%20was%20decided%20not%20to%20bring%20the%20white%20paper%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20economy%20in%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20interest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20suggestions%20coming%20up%20that%20I%20should%20lay%20a%20White%20Paper%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20economy.%20But%20I%20am%20not%20doing%20it%20because%20of%20national%20interest%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20quoted%20Modi%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20if%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy%20would%20have%20come%20out%20then%2C%20not%20a%20single%20investor%20would%20have%20come%20and%20our%20own%20citizens%20would%20have%20asked%20what%20was%20going%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitharaman%20said%20that%20during%20the%20UPA%20years%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbig%20ticket%20corruption%20was%20one%20a%20year%2C%20so%20our%20own%20citizens%20would%20have%20lost%20confidence%20in%20the%20economy%20because%20of%20the%20white%20paper.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%2010%20years%20which%20can%20be%20periodically%20compared%20to%20UPA%E2%80%99s%2010%20years.%20Responsibly%2C%20we%20took%20the%20challenge%20of%20getting%20everything%20sorted%20out.%20Now%2C%20having%20placed%20the%20economy%20in%20a%20better%20position%2C%20we%20have%20come%20up%20with%20the%20white%20paper%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChallenging%20the%20opposition%2C%20Sitharaman%20said%20that%20the%20document%20is%20based%20on%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20challenge%20anyone%20who%20says%20this%20document%20is%20baseless.%20Everything%20is%20with%20evidence.%20I%20challenge%20anyone%20who%20says%20that%20we%20have%20kept%20the%20White%20Paper%20which%20has%20no%20proof%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Concoction%20of%20lies%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20MPs%20during%20their%20speeches%20questioned%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20white%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPremachandran%2C%20who%20had%20also%20moved%20a%20motion%20disapproving%20it%2C%20said%20during%20his%20speech%20that%20the%20white%20paper%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20attempt%20to%20ignore%20the%20valuable%20efforts%20of%20the%20previous%20UPA%20government%20and%20the%20contributions%20of%20renowned%20economists%20and%20scientists%20and%20experts%20from%202004%20to%202014.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20in%20the%20last%20decade%20the%20country%20has%20seen%20growth%20of%20unemployment%2C%20inflation%2C%20price%20rise%20and%20increase%20in%20poverty%20and%20%E2%80%9Cshifting%20the%20blame%20on%20to%20the%20previous%20government%20for%20failures%20of%20this%20government%20is%20not%20proper.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETMC%E2%80%99s%20Roy%20who%20had%20moved%20the%20second%20motion%20disapproving%20the%20white%20paper%20said%20that%20the%20the%20finance%20minister%20should%20have%20first%20apoligised%20to%20the%20nation%20for%20demonetisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20not%20been%20a%20bigger%20scam%20in%20the%20history%20of%20this%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20pointing%20to%20the%20cash%20in%20circulation%20returning%20to%20the%20economy%20after%20the%20circulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERay%20also%20demanded%20to%20know%20what%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20extradite%20fugitive%20economic%20offenders%20like%20Nirav%20Modi%2C%20Mehul%20Choksi%20and%20Vijay%20Mallya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20the%20poorest%20among%20BRICS%20nations.%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20India%20grow%20as%20per%20its%20potential%3F%20Why%20are%20we%20behind%20China%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20little%20growth%20in%20jobs%20and%20manufacturing%2C%20Roy%20said%20only%20%E2%80%9Ca%20few%20well%20connected%20families%20have%20accounted%20for%20significant%20growth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGovernment%20has%20no%20answers%20on%20unemployment%2C%20demonetisation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%E2%80%99%20leader%20of%20the%20house%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Choudhury%20said%20that%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20white%20paper%20shows%20that%20it%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Celection%20manifesto%E2%80%9D%20to%20tarnish%20the%20image%20of%20the%20UPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20intent%20and%20purpose%20of%20bringing%20this%20kind%20of%20White%20Paper%20simply%20is%20not%20convincing.%20It%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20sheer%20concoction%2C%20rather%20a%20granary%20of%20concoctions%20and%20mountain%20of%20lies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20fag%20end%20of%20the%20session%2C%20this%20kind%20of%20white%20paper%20only%20with%20the%20objective%20to%20tarnish%20the%20ten%20years%20of%20UPA%20government%2C%20does%20not%20cut%20ice.%20It%20is%20nothing%20but%20an%20electoral%20manifesto%20with%20the%20objective%20of%20scoring%20electoral%20brownie%20points%20that%20has%20prompted%20you%20to%20bring%20this%20kind%20of%20white%20paper.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIMIM%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20demanded%20to%20know%20from%20the%20finance%20minister%20who%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20declining%20GDP%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGDP%20growth%20during%20UPA%20was%206.8%25%20on%20average%2C%20during%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20government%20it%20is%205.9%25%20on%20average%2C%20tell%20us%20is%20China%20responsible%20or%20Pakistan%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20government%20of%20%E2%80%9Chiding%20data%E2%80%9D%20Owaisi%20asked%20why%20Unemployment%20Survey%20done%20since%202011%20and%20the%20PLF%20survey%20(National%20Survey%20Organization%E2%80%99s%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey)%20and%20consumption%20survey%20that%20happened%20in%202018%20and%202017%20respectively%20have%20not%20been%20done%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCP%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20said%20that%20while%20a%20white%20paper%20usually%20covers%20an%20issue%20in-depth%2C%20and%20ways%20to%20resolve%20a%20problem%2C%20the%20white%20paper%20brought%20by%20the%20government%20only%20included%20%E2%80%9Callegations%E2%80%9D%20against%20the%20previous%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20a%20white%20paper%2C%20it%20is%20a%20politically%20coloured%20paper%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMK%20MP%20DNV%20Senthilkumar%20S%20called%20the%20white%20paper%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwolf%20in%20sheep%E2%80%99s%20clothing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20white%20paper%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20concoction%20of%20twisted%20facts%20and%20selective%20memory%20conveniently%20ignoring%20the%20failures%20of%20the%20present%20administration.%20The%20honourable%20prime%20minister%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20penchant%20for%20blaming%20the%20Congress%20and%20Nehru%20for%20everything.%20They%20have%20been%20in%20power%20for%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20and%20they%20are%20supposed%20to%20talk%20about%20their%20merits%20and%20their%20success%20but%20they%20still%20want%20to%20talk%20about%20Congress%20and%20Nehru%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInflation%2C%20jobs%20and%20leadership%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitharaman%20in%20her%20reply%20said%20that%20under%20the%20UPA%20average%20annual%20inflation%20was%208.2%25%2C%20and%20that%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20it%20has%20averaged%209.8%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20the%20UPA%2C%20retail%20inflation%20was%20more%20than%209%25%20for%2022%20months%2C%20our%20retail%20inflation%20was%20mostly%20at%205%25%2C%20never%20crossed%208%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitharaman%20claimed%20that%20in%20the%20Modi%20years%2C%20unemployment%20has%20recorded%20a%20decrease%20from%205.8%25%20in%202018-19%2C%20to%203.2%25%20in%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Bloomberg%20that%20cited%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Funemployment-rate-rose-to-10-09-percent-in-october-cmie-data%5C%22%3ECentre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy%20(CMIE)%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20India%E2%80%99s%20unemployment%20rate%20rose%20to%20a%20two-year%20high%20of%2010.09%25%20in%20October%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20over%208%20lakh%20central%20government%20vacancies%20had%20been%20filled%20with%20%E2%80%9Ccomplete%20transparency%E2%80%9D%20while%20the%20gig%20economy%20had%20created%2077%20lakh%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Santosh%20Mehrotra%20wrote%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fwhat-we-know-about-indias-post-covid-economy-recovery-and-rising-inequality%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20open%20unemployment%20was%20barely%202.1%25%20in%202012%20(the%20last%20year%20for%20which%20data%20was%20available%20before%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power)%20and%20had%20already%20nearly%20tripled%20to%206.1%25%20in%202018%20(National%20Survey%20Organization%E2%80%99s%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey%20(PLFS)%2C%20conducted%20annually%20since%202017-18)%2C%20the%20highest%20rate%20in%2045%20years%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20labour%20force%20surveys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitharaman%20also%20accused%20the%20opposition%20Congress%20of%20wanting%20credit%20for%20schemes%20like%20MGNREGA%2C%20DBT%20and%20Aadhaar%20but%20claimed%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CUIDAI%E2%80%99s%20parent%20body%20in%20UPA%2C%20the%20Planning%20Commission%2C%20was%20rejecting%20its%20proposal%20of%20Rs%2015%2C000%20crore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20least%20three%20ministries%20at%20that%20time%20had%20serious%20reservations%20with%20real-time%20bio-metric%20authentication%20but%20Congress%20still%20says%20that%20%E2%80%98Aadhaar%20is%20ours.%E2%80%99%20It%20was%20said%20that%20UIDAI%20was%20%E2%80%98conceptualised%20with%20no%20clarity%20of%20purpose%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20it%20was%20due%20to%20Aadhaar%20%26amp%3B%20DBT%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20was%20able%20to%20send%20money%20directly%20into%20beneficiaries%E2%80%99%20accounts%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20leadership%20and%20vision%20which%20the%20UPA%20completely%20lacked%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20embracing%20Aadhaar%2C%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202014%20elections%2C%20however%2C%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20including%20Modi%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fcurrent-affairs%2Faadhaar-gets-a-second-life-from-modi-114102800024_1.html%5C%22%3Erallied%20against%20Aadhaar%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20criticised%20the%20biometric%20identity%20card%20as%20a%20waste%20of%20taxpayers%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707499157000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F24160818%2FScreenshot-2023-03-24-at-4.07.15-PM_cleanup.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Felection-manifesto-says-opposition-as-lok-sabha-discusses-centres-white-paper-on-economy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Challenging%20the%20opposition%20to%20prove%20that%20the%20white%20paper%20is%20%E2%80%98baseless%E2%80%99%20Union%20minister%20of%20finance%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20said%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98serious%20document%E2%80%99%20and%20quoted%20prime%20minister%20Modi%20in%202016%20to%20say%20that%20it%20was%20decided%20not%20to%20bring%20the%20white%20paper%20earlier%20in%20'national%20interest'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Felection-manifesto-says-opposition-as-lok-sabha-discusses-centres-white-paper-on-economy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hyundai%20Motor%20picks%20JPMorgan%2C%20Citi%20to%20accelerate%20%243%20billion%20IPO%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707499033000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-11%2F03%2Ffull%2F1667496070-3112.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhyundai-motor-picks-jpmorgan-citi-to-accelerate-3-billion-ipo-report-124020901434_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20company%20plans%20to%20file%20regulatory%20papers%20in%20India%20by%20May%20to%20June%20for%20an%20approval%2C%20said%20two%20of%20the%20three%20sources%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20declined%20to%20be%20named%20as%20the%20talks%20are%20private%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhyundai-motor-picks-jpmorgan-citi-to-accelerate-3-billion-ipo-report-124020901434_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhyundai-motor-picks-jpmorgan-citi-to-accelerate-3-billion-ipo-report-124020901434_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhyundai-motor-picks-jpmorgan-citi-to-accelerate-3-billion-ipo-report-124020901434_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BChose%20Rashtraneeti%20Over%20Rajneeti%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20On%20Why%20White%20Paper%20Was%20Brought%20Now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Friday%20said%20his%20government%20could%20have%20brought%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20economy%20in%202014%20itself%20when%20it%20came%20to%20power%20but%20he%20chose%20'rashtraneeti'%20over%20'rajneeti'%20as%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20shake%20the%20country's%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20has%20been%20introduced%20in%20the%20last%20Parliament%20session%20before%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi-led%20government%20on%20Thursday%20brought%20a%20white%20paper%20tearing%20into%20Congress-led%20UPA%20rule%20and%20saying%20that%20it%20had%20turned%20the%20Indian%20economy%20into%20a%20non-performing%20one%20through%20indiscriminate%20revenue%20expenditure%2C%20off%20budget%20borrowings%20and%20pile%20of%20bad%20debts%20at%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20Times%20Groups'%20ET%20NOW%20Global%20Business%20Summit%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20that%20in%20the%20decade%20before%202014%2C%20the%20policies%20on%20which%20the%20country%20was%20running%20was%20taking%20the%20country%20on%20the%20path%20of%20bankruptcy.%20%26quot%3BOn%20this%2C%20we%20have%20tabled%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20the%20economy%20in%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20discussion%20on%20it%20is%20ongoing.%20Since%20there%20is%20such%20a%20big%20audience%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20state%20my%20'Mann%20ki%20Baat'%20also%20that%20the%20white%20paper%20that%20I%20have%20brought%20now%2C%20I%20could%20have%20brought%20in%202014.%20If%20my%20aim%20had%20been%20to%20derive%20political%20gain%2C%20then%20I%20would%20have%20kept%20those%20figures%20before%20the%20people%2010%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20things%20came%20before%20me%20in%202014%2C%20I%20was%20stunned.%20The%20economy%20was%20in%20a%20critical%20situation.%20Due%20to%20scams%20and%20policy%20paralysis%2C%20there%20was%20widespread%20pessimism%20among%20global%20investors.%20If%20I%20would%20have%20brought%20these%20things%20to%20light%2C%20if%20a%20wrong%20signal%20would%20have%20gone%2C%20probably%20the%20country%20would%20have%20lost%20its%20confidence%20in%20the%20country%20like%20when%20a%20patient%20gets%20to%20know%20that%20he%20has%20a%20serious%20disease%2C%20he%20panics%2C%20and%20the%20country%20would%20have%20felt%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prime%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20that%20bringing%20the%20white%20paper%20in%202014%20would%20have%20suited%20him%20politically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'Rajniti'%20tells%20me%20to%20do%20that%20but%20'Rashtraneeti'%20does%20not%20allow%20me%20to%20do%20that%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20I%20chose%20'rashtraneeti'%20over%20'rajneeti'.%20And%20when%20the%20situation%20has%20become%20strong%20in%2010%20years%20and%20we%20can%20sustain%20any%20assault%2C%20then%20I%20thought%20I%20should%20tell%20the%20truth%20to%20the%20people%20and%20that%20is%20why%20I%20released%20white%20paper%20in%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20look%20at%20it%2C%20you%20will%20know%20where%20we%20were%20and%20from%20what%20situation%20we%20have%20risen%20and%20reached%20here.%20Now%20you%20are%20seeing%20the%20new%20height%20of%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20it%20is%20his%20guarantee%20that%20in%20his%20third%20term%2C%20India%20will%20become%20the%20world's%20third%20largest%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20summit%2C%20Times%20Group%20MD%20Vineet%20Jain%20said%20the%20last%20ten%20years%C2%A0have%20been%20transformative%20for%20India%20with%20its%20economy%20undergoing%20significant%20structural%20reforms%2C%20boosting%20its%20macroeconomic%20foundations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20embark%20on%20'Amritkaal'%2C%20I%20want%20us%20all%20to%20envision%20a%20futuristic%2C%20inclusive%2C%20and%20prosperous%20society%20rooted%20in%20a%20human-centric%20approach.%20This%20will%20be%20our%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20two%20decades%20belong%20to%20India%2C%20where%20initiatives%20like%20Make%20in%20India%2C%20Create%20in%20India%2C%20Serve%20from%20India%2C%20and%20Start%20up%20India%20converge%20into%20a%20majestic%20narrative%2C%20transforming%20the%20nation%20into%20a%20knowledge%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20manufacturing%20hub%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20vision%20aligns%2