JP%20government%20has%20levelled%20the%20same%20allegation%20at%20the%20Congress%20government%20which%20came%20to%20power%20last%20year%2C%20but%20with%20a%20twist.%20The%20association%20has%20said%20that%20instead%20of%20politicians%20making%20money%2C%20it%20is%20bureaucrats%20who%20are%20doing%20so%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20has%20used%20the%20opportunity%20to%20attack%20the%20Congress%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20has%20said%20the%20contractors'%20body%20must%20present%20proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20association's%20allegations%20in%202022%20had%20led%20to%20the%20Congress%20terming%20the%20BJP%20regime%20in%20the%20state%20a%20'40%25%20sarkara'%20(40%25%20government).%20The%20party%20also%20launched%20a%20'PayCM'%20campaign%20with%20a%20QR%20code%20leading%20to%20a%20'40%25%20sarkara'%20website%2C%20which%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20was%20charging%2040%25%20commission%20on%20public%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20had%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20Congress%20storming%20back%20to%20power%20in%20Karnataka%20in%20May%20last%20year%2C%20winning%20135%20of%20224%20Assembly%20seats.%20The%20claims%20against%20the%20Congress%20government%20have%20come%20just%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ED%20Kempanna%2C%20President%2C%20Karnataka%20State%20Contractors'%20Association%2C%20who%20had%20complained%20about%20corruption%20in%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20corruption%20has%20come%20down.%20Now%2C%20officials%20are%20making%20money.%20Earlier%2C%20politicians%20were.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20members%20of%20the%20association%20alleged%20that%20officials%20don't%20issue%20work%20orders%20or%20release%20money%20unless%20bribes%20are%20paid%20and%20also%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3Bpackage%20deals%26quot%3B%20are%20awarded%20to%20agencies%20close%20to%20the%20bureaucrats%2C%20ignoring%20local%20contractors.%3C%2Fp%