inted.%20Mr.%20Modi%20said%20the%20Commission%20should%20change%20its%20approach%20and%20allocate%20higher%20funds%20to%20the%20states%20that%20contribute%20more%20to%20the%20national%20GDP%20with%20a%20view%20to%20give%20impetus%20to%20the%20development%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20infrastructural%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20suggested%20a%20new%20formula%20for%20the%20allocation%20of%20funds%20to%20the%20states%2C%20which%20should%20be%20based%20on%20%E2%80%9C25%25%20based%20on%20population%2C%205%25%20based%20on%20migration%2C%2010%25%20based%20on%20area%2C%2035%25%20based%20on%20the%20fiscal%20capacity%20distance%2C%205%25%20based%20on%20state%E2%80%99s%20contribution%20in%20national%20economy%20and%2020%25%20based%20on%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20fiscal%20discipline.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20in%20October%202013%2C%20in%20his%20meeting%20with%20the%2014th%20Finance%20Commission%2C%20the%20then%20Gujarat%20chief%20minister%20Modi%20demanded%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fmodi-anger-with-centre-justified-bjp%2Farticleshow%2F3124848.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20Central%20government%20should%20provide%2050%25%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20its%20tax%20revenues%20to%20the%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWas%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20trying%20to%20break%20the%20country%20as%20a%20chief%20minister%3F%20Did%20the%20poorer%20states%20not%20need%20the%20help%20of%20their%20richer%20counterparts%3F%20These%20are%20questions%20worth%20pondering%20over%2C%20as%20the%20BJP%20has%20fiercely%20attacked%20the%20opposition%20for%20protesting%20to%20secure%20its%20fiscal%20rights.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707490796000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18121214%2FGDpRC6Va