0on%20a%20transformative%20journey%20with%20a%20series%20of%20economic%20reforms%20that%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20shaping%20the%20middle%20class%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20behalf%20of%20Indian%20National%20Congress%2C%20we%20welcome%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20being%20conferred%20to%20Shri%20P%20V%20Narasimha%20Rao%2C%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20and%20Dr%20M%20S%20Swaminathan.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn1.%20Former%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Former%20Congress%20President%2C%20Shri%20P%20V%20Narasimha%20Rao%20has%20tremendously%20contributed%20to%20nation%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20(%40kharge)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%2Fstatus%2F1755901051553947747%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20Mr%20Rao%20made%20significant%20contributions%20to%20India's%20Nuclear%20programme%20and%20his%20tenure%20was%20marked%20by%20a%20number%20of%20foreign%20policy%20achievements%2C%20including%20the%20'Look%20East'%20policy%2C%20the%20Congress%20chief%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BHis%20vital%20role%20in%20the%20prosperity%20and%20development%20of%20our%20nation%20shall%20always%20be%20cherished%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20%26quot%3Ba%20son%20of%20the%20soil%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20he%20had%20helped%20strengthen%20rural%20India.%20He%20also%20praised%20Dr%20Swaminathan%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20institution%20builder%20par%20excellence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20party%20applauds%20their%20vision%2C%20their%20hardwork%20and%20the%20exceptional%20legacies%20of%20these%20national%20icons%2C%20which%20the%20nation%20has%20always%20celebrated%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20president%20posted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20when%20she%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20announcements%2C%20specifically%20for%20Rao%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20welcome%20them...%20why%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20former%20Union%20minister%20P%20Chidambaram%20welcomed%20the%20announcement%2C%20he%20also%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20BJP%2C%20stating%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20discovering%26quot%3B%20the%20contribution%20of%20the%20three%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHappy%20that%20secular%2C%20socialist%20leaders%20have%20been%20awarded%20Bharat%20Ratna.%20It%20is%20gratifying%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20discovering%20the%20contribution%20of%20the%20three%20eminent%20men%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHappy%20that%20secular%2C%20socialist%20leaders%20have%20been%20awarded%20Bharat%20Ratna%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20is%20gratifying%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20discovering%20the%20contribution%20of%20the%20three%20eminent%20men%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20is%20of%20no%20consequence%20to%20me%20that%20the%20recognition%20has%20come%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20general%20elections.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHomage%20to%20the%20memory%20of%20the%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20P.%20Chidambaram%20(%40PChidambaram_IN)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPChidambaram_IN%2Fstatus%2F1755915282332135456%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20of%20no%20consequence%20to%20me%20that%20the%20recognition%20has%20come%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20general%20elections.%20Homage%20to%20the%20memory%20of%20the%20three%20Bharat%20Ratna%20Awardees%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnpacking%20The%20Politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20have%20often%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20%26quot%3Bdisrespecting%26quot%3B%20Narasimha%20Rao%2C%20and%20the%20PM%20has%20also%20accused%20the%20party%20of%20%26quot%3Bignoring%26quot%3B%20the%20leader%20to%20serve%20its%20purpose%20of%20glorifying%20one%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chidambaram's%20reference%20to%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20general%20elections%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20allusion%20to%20comments%20by%20some%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20hoping%20to%20reap%20political%20benefits%20from%20awarding%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20to%20Rao%2C%20who%20was%20the%20first%20person%20from%20south%20India%20to%20become%20prime%20minister.%20Rao%20was%20from%20undivided%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20southern%20region%20is%20the%20only%20part%20of%20the%20country%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20seen%20as%20being%20on%20the%20back%20foot%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707487980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fgsbb0e68_pv-narasimha-rao_625x300_09_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-welcomes-bharat-ratna-to-narasimha-rao-but-sneaks-in-a-dig-at-bjp-5026187%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%2C%20which%20is%20accused%20by%20the%20BJP%20of%20disrespecting%20its%20own%20leader%20Narasimha%20Rao%2C%20has%20welcomed%20the%20announcement%20that%20the%20government%20will%20confer%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20on%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%20-%20but%20not%20without%20taking%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20ruling%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-welcomes-bharat-ratna-to-narasimha-rao-but-sneaks-in-a-dig-at-bjp-5026187%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-welcome