andir%20some%20years%20ago.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20parliament%20of%20Hindu%20Gods%2C%20they%20may%20formally%20welcome%20a%20new%20entrant%20into%20their%20fraternity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EScholars%20say%20the%20concept%20of%20God-King%20is%20rooted%20in%20the%20indigenous%20tradition.%20They%20used%20to%20say%20this%20about%20democracy.%20It%20has%20been%20said%20that%20history%20is%20a%20fluid%20creature%20and%20is%20easily%20contaminated.%20Authoritarian%20regimes%20edit%20and%20airbrush%20history%20books%20as%20the%20key%20to%20political%20legitimacy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20narratives%20about%20the%20Babri%20Mosque%20and%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20validate%20this%20view.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20has%20emerged%20as%20an%20object%20of%20veneration.%20L.K.%20Advani%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20one-time%20top%20leader%2C%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Flord-ram-has-chosen-pm-modi-to-build-his-temple-lk-advani%2Farticle67735436.ece%5C%22%3EModi%20was%20chosen%20by%20God%20as%20his%20instrument%20for%20the%20Ayodhya%20event%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CGod%E2%80%99s%20instrument%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20term%20used%20by%20Modi%20for%20himself%20in%20his%20election%20speeches.%20Time%20and%20again%2C%20he%20highlights%20his%20connection%20with%20the%20Divine.%20He%20hears%20the%20call%20of%20the%20Divine.%20One%20widely%20circulated%20poster%20shows%20the%20life-sized%20Modi%20escorting%20child%20Ram%20back%20to%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20Cabinet%20members%20joined%20in%20the%20worship%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMahamanav%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20superman%20%E2%80%93%20who%20presides%20over%20their%20meetings.%20They%20expressed%20their%20feeling%20of%20spiritual%20bliss%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eaatmic%20anand%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20flowing%20from%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20feat.%20They%20adopted%20a%20resolution%20calling%20Modi%20the%20harbinger%20of%20a%20new%20era%20who%20achieved%20what%20the%20Indian%20civilisation%20had%20dreamt%20of%20for%20500%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20called%20Modi%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfifth%20Shankaracharya%E2%80%9D%20because%20he%20took%20the%20prime%20position%20at%20the%20religious%20ceremony.%20This%20goes%20against%20a%20basic%20tenet%20of%20Hinduism%20that%20each%20person%20should%20follow%20his%20or%20own%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edharma%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20specific%20duty%2C%20and%20conduct.%20The%20king%20should%20follow%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eraj%20dharma%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20a%20priest%20or%20saint%20should%20do%20his%20religious%20duties.%20But%20in%20this%20strange%20scenario%2C%20religious%20leaders%20are%20making%20political%20statements%20and%20a%20prime%20minister%20is%20lecturing%20on%20religious%20matters%20and%20talking%20of%20the%20divine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20mobilised%20the%20people%20all%20over%20India%20by%20calling%20upon%20them%20to%20light%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ediyas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20January%2022.%20The%20BJP%20wants%20the%20%E2%80%9Creturn%E2%80%9D%20of%20Ram%20to%20be%20remembered%20by%20the%20masses%20till%20the%20coming%20parliamentary%20elections.%20Modi%20thinks%20big.%20He%20says%20the%20day%20will%20be%20remembered%20for%20a%20thousand%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20speech%20at%20the%20consecration%2C%20Modi%20talked%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EKalachakra%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20He%20did%20not%20explain%20whether%20it%20was%20simply%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20Wheel%20of%20Time%20or%20to%20the%20intricate%20Buddhist%20tantric%20practice.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20speech%20writer%20must%20have%20studied%20the%20generation%20stage%20of%20this%20practice%20involving%20the%20visualisation%20of%20oneself%20as%20a%20deity%20within%20the%20context%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emandala%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20There%20is%20no%20interest%20in%20complex%20theology%2C%20so%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EKalachakra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20not%20discussed%20in%20social%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ayodhya%20spectacle%20was%20organised%20on%20a%20grand%20scale.%20The%20state%20played%20a%20big%20role.%20It%20deployed%20thousands%20of%20folk%20artistes%20to%20entertain%20the%20guests.%20Half%20a%20day%E2%80%99s%20holiday%20was%20declared%20by%20government%20offices%20on%20January%2022.%20Devotional%20songs%20were%20played%20on%20the%20TV%20channels%20and%20through%20loudspeakers.%20Life-size%20cut-outs%20of%20Modi%20were%20seen%20hanging%20on%20the%20roadside%20poles.%20Millions%20of%20saffron%20flags%20were%20waved%20with%20exultation%20and%20with%20hostility%20towards%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20other%E2%80%9D.%20Knowing%20what%20Modi%20stands%20for%2C%20they%20demonstrated%20fake%20religiosity%20on%20roads%20and%20in%20colonies%20without%20fearing%20police%20action.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20wave%20of%20triumphalism%20led%20them%20to%20shout%20provocative%20slogans%20in%20front%20of%20Muslims%20in%20Mumbai%20which%20led%20to%20violent%20clashes.%20Some%20mosques%20attracted%20mobs%20shouting%20that%20every%20child%20must%20say%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EJai%20Shri%20Ram%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%9D%20A%20gag%20asked%20the%20government%20to%20build%20more%20mosques%20because%20what%20Ram%20devotees%20like%20most%20is%20to%20chant%20outside%20mosques.%20Elsewhere%2C%20Ram%20devotees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmp-right-wing-activists-plant-saffron-flag-on-the-holy-cross-on-the-eve-of-ram-temple-ceremony%5C%22%3Eclimbed%20atop%20a%20church%20and%20planted%20a%20saffron%20flag%20above%20the%20cross%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20set%20pattern%20of%20organised%20lumpenisation%20and%20religious%20polarisation%20marks%20Indian%20democracy.%20Mobocracy%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20dirty%20word.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22190217%2Fimage-1781.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22998%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22190217%2Fimage-1781.png%20998w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22190217%2Fimage-1781-300x216.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694031%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERight-wing%20activists%20plant%20a%20saffron%20flag%20atop%20a%20holy%20cross%2C%20in%20Jhabua%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20on%20January%2021%2C%202024.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ayodhya%20spectacle%20served%20the%20purpose%20of%20energising%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20base%20through%20a%20religious%20show.%20Drowning%20in%20the%20rising%20sea%20of%20faith%2C%20Hindus%20admired%20the%20razzmatazz%20of%20the%20epoch-making%20politico-religious%20carnival.%20They%20were%20struck%20by%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20sartorial%20elegance%2C%20his%20event%20management%2C%20and%20his%20effort%20to%20remain%20in%20front%20of%20the%20camera%20lens.%20Even%20while%20praying%2C%20he%20faces%20the%20camera%20while%20the%20idol%20is%20on%20his%20side.%20Modi%20hates%20to%20show%20his%20back%20to%20the%20camera.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20shiny%20Ayodhya%20temple%20saw%20politicians%2C%20singers%2C%20dancers%2C%20decorators%2C%20celebrities%2C%20film%20stars%2C%20choreographers%2C%20speech-writers%2C%20saints%2C%20and%20billionaires.%20Masons%20and%20carpenters%20will%20be%20back%20to%20complete%20the%20temple.%20Some%20say%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Ffull-text-only-political-hindus-are-happy-shankaracharya-on-ayodhya-ram-temple-consecration%5C%22%3Etheir%20work%20will%20defile%20the%20consecrated%20temple%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20transformation%20has%20impressed%20all%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftemple-construction-meant-small-business-owners-in-ayodhya-lost-money-and-hope%5C%22%3Ebarring%20those%20whose%20houses%20were%20destroyed%20for%20widening%20the%20roads%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20demolition%20of%20small%20temples%20and%20mosques%20for%20the%20same%20purpose%20did%20not%20hurt%20religious%20sentiments%20this%20time!%20The%20temple%20town%20now%20has%20an%20airport%20and%20new%20luxury%20hotels.%20The%20Vatican%20will%20have%20to%20spruce%20itself%2C%20to%20compete%20with%20the%20Hindu%20Vatican.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22132101%2FSG6.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22936%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22132101%2FSG6.jpg%20936w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22132101%2FSG6-300x194.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693965%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22604%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPosters%20and%20billboards%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%20ceremony.%20Photo%3A%20Sabah%20Gurmat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20political%20Hindutva%20was%20unleashed%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20wide%20gulf%20developed%20between%20liberal%20and%20conservative%20Hindus.%20The%20consecration%20divided%20even%20the%20devout%20Hindus.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20status%20in%20the%20ceremony%20was%20questioned%20by%20religious%20scholars%20who%20explained%20how%20consecration%20must%20be%20performed%20as%20per%20the%20sacred%20texts.%20Also%2C%20they%20questioned%20the%20decision%20to%20have%20it%20done%20in%20a%20temple%20that%20was%20incomplete.%20To%20telecast%20the%20image%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20camera%20was%20allowed%20inside%20the%20sanctum-sanctorum%20of%20the%20new%20Ram%20Temple%20which%20shocked%20the%20traditionalists.%20Consolidation%20of%20the%20Hindu%20votes%20is%20an%20essential%20element%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20strategy.%20But%20the%20rituals%20at%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20caused%20a%20rift%20among%20the%20Hindus%20instead%20of%20uniting%20them.%20This%20division%20may%20do%20no%20harm%20to%20Modi%20as%20these%20traditionalists%20will%20not%20vote%20for%20a%20secular%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20has%20reasons%20to%20be%20immensely%20satisfied%20with%20what%20he%20achieved%20by%20having%20the%20half-built%20temple%20consecrated%20before%20the%20parliamentary%20elections.%20Modi%20tracks%20his%20internal%20enemies%20and%20saw%20the%20challenge%20coming%20from%20Adityanath%2C%20fast%20emerging%20as%20a%20rival%20Hindutva%20icon.%20By%20demonstrating%20his%20pre-eminence%20in%20the%20temple%2C%20Modi%20cut%20the%20Yogi%20to%20size%20and%20ensured%20that%20the%20UP%20chief%20minster%20does%20not%20rob%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindu%20Hriday%20Samrat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20crown%20from%20him.%20Even%20the%20RSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20found%20it%20necessary%20to%20praise%20Modi%20for%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Etapasya%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20preceding%20the%20ceremony.%20Bhagwat%20will%20stop%20looking%20for%20an%20alternative%20to%20Modi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22185025%2FScreenshot-2024-01-22-at-12.41.27-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22185025%2FScreenshot-2024-01-22-at-12.41.27-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22185025%2FScreenshot-2024-01-22-at-12.41.27-PM-300x150.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22185025%2FScreenshot-2024-01-22-at-12.41.27-PM-1024x512.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22185025%2FScreenshot-2024-01-22-at-12.41.27-PM-800x400.png%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694025%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20takes%20part%20in%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Temple.%20Photo%3A%20Screenshot%20from%20DD%20News%20broadcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20roar%20of%20faith%20has%20sealed%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20ears%20to%20the%20voices%20of%20reason.%20Not%20to%20shout%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EJai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20an%20anti-national%20act.%20An%20Age%20of%20Superstitions%20has%20dawned.%20No%20Arya%20Samaj%20leader%20such%20as%20Swami%20Agnivesh%20countered%20such%20warnings.%20In%20the%20present%20atmosphere%2C%20no%20one%20will%20dare%20to%20write%20on%20how%20Ram%20behaved%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20a%20popular%20theme%20of%20feminist%20prose%20and%20poetry%20written%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20weird%20India%2C%20bizarre%20scenes%20are%20witnessed%20daily.%20Some%20feel%20embarrassed%20by%20all%20that%20is%20going%20on%2C%20such%20as%20an%20airline%20parading%20its%20crew%20dressed%20as%20Ram%2C%20Laxman%20and%20Sita%20or%20the%20government%20buses%20playing%20songs%20in%20praise%20of%20Ram.%20Those%20Hindus%20who%20are%20not%20attracted%20to%20Hindutva%20feel%20anguished%20about%20the%20mixing%20of%20religion%20with%20politics%2C%20violent%20assertion%20of%20majoritarianism%2C%20oppression%20of%20a%20minority%20and%20progressive%20destruction%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20secular%20constitution.%20Many%20live%20in%20fear.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECritics%20say%20the%20governments%20focus%20on%20religious%20issues%2C%20doing%20little%20about%20widespread%20poverty%2C%20hunger%2C%20and%20ill-health.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhospitals-january-22-ram-temple-holiday-surgeries-opd%5C%22%3ESome%20hospitals%20in%20Delhi%20decide%20to%20close%20for%20half%20a%20day%20because%20of%20the%20ceremony%20in%20the%20distant%20town%20of%20Ayodhya%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20later%20withdraws%20that%20order%20in%20the%20face%20of%20protests.%20Many%20unprivileged%20Hindus%20keep%20telling%20the%20TV%20interviewers%20that%20they%20want%20jobs%2C%20hospitals%2C%20and%20schools%2C%20not%20temples.%20An%20old%20cartoon%20by%20R.K.%20Laxman%20shows%20the%20board%20of%20a%20government-run%20%E2%80%9CTemple%20and%20Mosque%20Construction%20Company%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20the%20common%20man%20outside%20asking%20when%20the%20nation%20will%20be%20built!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EObserving%20the%20quest%20for%20personal%20power%20in%20India%20bordering%20on%20imperialism%2C%20one%20recalls%20Rudyard%20Kipling%E2%80%99s%20story%20and%20the%20famous%20film%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Man%20Who%20Would%20Be%20King%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20growing%20tribalism%20and%20the%20emergence%20of%20a%20new%20god%20in%20India%20remind%20of%20Kafiristan.%20Kipling%20has%20written%20about%20two%20British%20rogue%20soldiers%20who%20took%20over%20Kafiristan%2C%20whose%20tribe%2C%20mesmerised%20by%20the%20white%20skin%2C%20anointed%20one%20of%20them%20as%20god.%20The%20white%20Britisher%20is%20subsequently%20found%20out%20because%20he%20marries%20a%20tribal%20woman.%20Out%20of%20fright%2C%20she%20bites%20him%20and%20his%20bleeding%20face%20makes%20the%20tribe%20realise%20that%20he%20is%20no%20God%20but%20a%20mortal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20has%20ensured%20that%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%20does%20not%20remain%20untouched%20by%20his%20magic.%20The%20wave%20of%20triumphalism%20reached%20distant%20lands%20and%20some%20Am-Indians%20in%20New%20York%20took%20out%20a%20procession%20hailing%20Ram%20and%20shouting%20an%20old%20slogan%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAyodhya%20to%20jhanki%20hai%2C%20Kashi%2C%20Mathura%20baaqi%20hai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20reminding%20Indians%20that%20they%20must%20do%20the%20same%20to%20the%20mosques%20in%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHindutva%20activists%20have%20already%20turned%20their%20attention%20to%20mosques%20in%20other%20towns.%20It%20is%20being%20said%20that%20Hindus%20have%20%E2%80%9Cwoken%20up%E2%80%9D%20after%20centuries%20of%20sleep.%20God%20forbid%20if%20groups%20of%20Jains%2C%20Buddhists%20or%20Muslims%20were%20to%20emerge%20to%20agitate%20against%20their%20places%20of%20worship%20that%20were%20turned%20into%20Hindu%20temples.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20official%20march%20towards%20establishing%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20has%20an%20external%20aspect.%20Such%20events%20are%20criticised%20by%20foreign%20media%20and%20send%20signals%20of%20religious%20intolerance%20in%20India.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20policies%20have%20justified%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20theocratic%20Pakistan.%20India%20keeps%20losing%20one%20battle%20of%20ideas%20after%20another.%20First%2C%20by%20becoming%20a%20Hindu%20Pakistan%20and%20then%20by%20reshaping%20an%20ancient%20faith%20tradition%20as%20Abrahamic%20Hinduism!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWords%20of%20wisdom%20come%20from%20a%20villager%20in%20Haryana.%20He%20says%20what%20a%20scholar%20could%20have%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CModi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Hinduism%20continued%20to%20survive%20centuries%20of%20foreign%20rule%20because%20religion%20was%20not%20associated%20with%20the%20ruler.%20If%20it%20were%20associated%20with%20a%20Prime%20Minister%20or%20President%20or%20King%2C%20it%20would%20have%20died%20after%20his%20departure.%20So%20please%20keep%20it%20out%20of%20your%20politics!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EL.K.%20Sharma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20author.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707486540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F23093839%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-19-at-21.24.54.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmodis-strange-india-of-celebrations-and-superstition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20this%20weird%20India%2C%20bizarre%20scenes%20are%20witnessed%20daily.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmodis-strange-india-of-celebrations-and-superstition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%2C%20RBI%20controversy%3A%20How%20will%20it%20impact%20the%20customers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707486510000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-02%2F05%2Ffull%2F1707154504-4958.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpaytm-payments-bank-rbi-controversy-how-will-it-impact-the-customers-124020901485_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20company%2C%20part%20of%20One97%20Communications%2C%20is%20a%20leader%20in%20Indian%20fintech%20and%20faces%20challenges%20of%20regulatory%20scrutiny%20and%20cus