-bharat-ratna-5025117%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchaudhary-charan-singh-bharat-ratna-jayant-chaudhary-rld-bjp-alliance-how-can-i-deny-rld-leader-on-bjp-deal-after-charan-singhs-bharat-ratna-5025117%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchaudhary-charan-singh-bharat-ratna-jayant-chaudhary-rld-bjp-alliance-how-can-i-deny-rld-leader-on-bjp-deal-after-charan-singhs-bharat-ratna-5025117%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Deleting%20'Secular'%2C%20'Socialist'%20From%20Preamble%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20Asks...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20questioned%20whether%20the%20Preamble%20of%20the%20Constitution%20could%20be%20amended%20while%20keeping%20the%20date%20of%20adoption%2C%20November%2026%2C%201949%2C%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Dipankar%20Datta%20posed%20the%20question%20to%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Subramanian%20Swamy%20and%20lawyer%20Vishnu%20Shankar%20Jain%2C%20who%20have%20sought%20deletion%20of%20the%20words%20%26quot%3BSocialist%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BSecular%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20Preamble%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20academic%20purpose%2C%20can%20a%20Preamble%20that%20has%20the%20date%20mentioned%2C%20be%20changed%20without%20altering%20the%20date%20of%20adoption.%20Otherwise%2C%20yes%20the%20Preamble%20can%20be%20amended.%20There%20is%20no%20problem%20with%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Datta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Swamy%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BThat's%20precisely%20the%20question%20in%20the%20matter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Datta%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20perhaps%20the%20only%20Preamble%20I%20have%20seen%20which%20comes%20with%20a%20date.%20We%20give%20this%20Constitution%20to%20us%20on%20so%20and%20so%20date%20...%20originally%20these%20two%20words%20(Socialist%20and%20Secular)%20were%20not%20there.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jain%20said%20that%20the%20Preamble%20of%20Constitution%20of%20India%20comes%20with%20a%20specific%20date%2C%20therefore%20it%20cannot%20be%20amended%20without%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Swamy%20intervened%20and%20said%20that%20the%2042nd%20Amendment%20Act%20was%20passed%20during%20the%20Emergency%20(1975-77).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanna%2C%20at%20the%20outset%2C%20told%20mr%20Swamy%20that%20the%20judges%20had%20received%20the%20case%20files%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20due%20to%20the%20paucity%20in%20time%2C%20they%20had%20not%20gone%20through%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20that%20the%20matter%20required%20detailed%20discussion%20and%20posted%20the%20hearing%20on%20the%20two%20petitions%20to%20April%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%202%2C%202022%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20tagged%20Mr%20Swamy's%20plea%20with%20anotther%20pending%20matter%20-%20filed%20by%20one%20Balram%20Singh%20and%20others%20-%20for%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Mr%20Swamy%20and%20Mr%20Singh%20have%20sought%20deletion%20of%20words%20%26quot%3BSocialist%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BSecular%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20Preamble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20words%20'Socialist'%20and%20'Secular'%20were%20inserted%20in%20the%20Preamble%20of%20the%20Constitution%20under%20the%2042nd%20Constitutional%20amendment%20moved%20by%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%20in%201976.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amendment%20changed%20the%20description%20of%20India%20in%20the%20Preamble%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Bsovereign%2C%20democratic%20republic%26quot%3B%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bsovereign%2C%20socialist%2C%20secular%2C%20democratic%20republic.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Swamy%2C%20in%20his%20petition%2C%20has%20contended%20that%20Preamble%20cannot%20be%20altered%2C%20varied%2C%20or%20repealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20in%20his%20petition%20that%20the%20Preamble%20not%20only%20indicated%20the%20essential%20features%20of%20the%20Constitution%20but%20also%20the%20fundamental%20conditions%20based%20on%20which%20it%20was%20adopted%20to%20create%20a%20unified%20integrated%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707475680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-11%2F2q980jqk_preamble_625x300_02_November_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-deleting-secular-socialist-from-preamble-supreme-court-asks-5025081%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20questioned%20whether%20the%20Preamble%20of%20the%20Constitution%20could%20be%20amended%20while%20keeping%20the%20date%20of%20adoption%2C%20November%2026%2C%201949%2C%20intact.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-deleting-secular-socialist-from-preamble-supreme-court-asks-5025081%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-deleting-secular-socialist-from-preamble-supreme-court-asks-5025081%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-deleting-secular-socialist-from-preamble-supreme-court-asks-5025081%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20happens%20if%20Biden%20decides%20to%20stand%20down%20-%20or%20if%20others%20try%20to%20make%20him%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707474540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F70x70%2Fskynews-joe-biden-washington_6449776.jpg%3F20240209143604%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwhat-would-happen-if-joe-biden-stood-down-how-the-race-to-be-the-democratic-party-nominee-would-unfold-13067310%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Can%20Joe%20Biden%20be%20replaced%20as%20the%20Democr