%20in%20making%20India%20economically%20advanced%2C%20laying%20a%20solid%20foundation%20for%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20prosperity%20and%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20award%20was%20also%20recently%20conferred%20upon%2096-year-old%20BJP%20veteran%20L.K.%20Advani.%20Socialist%20politician%20and%20two-time%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Karpoori%20Thakur%20was%20also%20posthumously%20recognised.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20news%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20highest%20civilian%20honour%20going%20to%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20has%20come%20amid%20reports%20of%20a%20seat-sharing%20deal%20between%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20(RLD)%20%E2%80%93%20founded%20by%20his%20son%20and%20now%20led%20by%20his%20grandson%2C%20Jayant%20Chaudhary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERLD%20president%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20reacted%20to%20the%20announcement%20on%20social%20media%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CDil%20jeet%20liya%20(hearts%20have%20been%20won).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20he%20was%20sealing%20a%20deal%20with%20NDA%20on%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20terms%2C%20Jayant%20did%20not%20deny%20joining%20hands%20with%20them.%20%E2%80%9CTalking%20about%20seats%20or%20votes%20will%20make%20this%20day%20less%20important.%20Such%20things%20don%E2%80%99t%20happen%20everyday%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20being%20asked%20if%20he%20was%20now%20closer%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20he%20gave%20another%20evasive%20reply%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20am%20congratulating%20%5BModi%5D%20and%20PM%20Modi%20has%20taken%20a%20decision%20which%20proves%20he%20understands%20the%20basic%20sentiments%20and%20character%20of%20the%20nation.%20Modiji%20has%20today%20won%20the%20heart%20of%20every%20follower%20of%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20%E2%80%93%20who%20confirmed%20an%20alliance%20with%20RLD%20last%20month%20%E2%80%93%20welcomed%20the%20award%20for%20Charan%20Singh%20but%20also%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20BJP%2C%20remarking%20that%20it%20is%20only%20right%20for%20someone%20who%20spent%20his%20life%20helping%20poor%20farmers%20get%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%E2%80%9D%2C%20NDTV%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchaudhary-charan-singh-bharat-ratna-jayant-chaudhary-rld-bjp-alliance-dil-jeet-liya-rld-leader-as-pm-announces-bharat-ratna-for-charan-singh-5024116%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20congratulate%20all%20farmers.%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singhji%20fought%20for%20farmers%20all%20his%20life%E2%80%A6%20We%20are%20happy%20a%20farmer%20leader%20got%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20the%20UP%20Assembly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20statement%20comes%20as%20the%20BJP%20faces%20yet%20another%20wave%20of%20farmer%20protests.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-on-their-way-to-protest-at-parliament-stopped-at-delhi-up-border%5C%22%3Efarmers%20from%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Noida%20and%20Greater%20Noida%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20cross%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20border%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20agitate%20for%20better%20land%20prices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707473499000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09153756%2FUntitled-design-9.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbharat-ratna-for-m-s-swaminathan-ex-pms-p-v-narasimha-rao-chaudhary-charan-singh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20news%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20highest%20civilian%20honour%20on%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20has%20come%20amid%20reports%20of%20a%20seat-sharing%20