h.%20Less%20than%2024%20hours%20after%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20chief%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fchandrababu-naidu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EN%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%3C%2Fa%3E%20met%20Home%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Famit-shah%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmit%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20BJP%20boss%20JP%20Nadda%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fjagan-mohan-reddy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYS%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%3C%2Fa%3E%20travelled%20to%20Delhi%20and%20met%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fpm-modi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20face%20of%20it%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20is%20meeting%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20discuss%20Special%20Category%20status%20for%20his%20state%20-%20a%20long-standing%20demand%20of%20his%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20and%20the%20TDP%20-%20central%20funds%20and%20other%20issues.%20Analysts%2C%20however%2C%20say%20the%20meeting%20suggests%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20its%20customary%20watch-and-wait%20mode%2C%20weighing%20its%20options%20before%20committing%20to%20either%20side%20(or%20remaining%20neutral)%20before%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20likely%2C%20any%20understanding%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20either%20the%20YSRCP%20or%20the%20TDP%20(which%20is%20allied%2C%20in%20the%20state%2C%20with%20actor%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20Jana%20Sena%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20national%20alliance)%20will%20be%20informal%2C%20which%20the%20regional%20parties%20may%20prefer%20since%20a%20formal%20tie-up%20risks%20them%20losing%20minority%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%2C%20interestingly%2C%20means%20neither%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20nor%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20wants%20the%20%3Cem%3Eswayamvar%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20end%20with%20a%20public%20marriage%3B%20a%20private%20handshake%20might%20be%20the%20preferred%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20be%20what%20the%20BJP%20wants%20too%2C%20despite%20Mr%20Modi's%20party%20not%20being%20a%20political%20force%20in%20the%20state%3B%20it%20was%20routed%20in%20the%202019%20Assembly%20election%2C%20failing%20to%20win%20a%20single%20seat%20despite%20contesting%20all%20173%20in%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20formal%20alliance%20with%20either%20party%20might%20be%20seen%20as%20favourable%20but%20that%20comes%20with%20its%20own%20challenges%2C%20the%20biggest%20of%20which%20is%20seat-sharing.%20Neither%20the%20YSRCP%20nor%20the%20TDP%20will%20be%20very%20keen%20on%20surrendering%20seats%20to%20the%20saffron%20party%2C%20because%20it%20reduces%20their%20potential%20contested%20seats-to-win%20ratio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20BJP%2C%20given%20its%20poor%20record%20from%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20its%20big%20defeat%20in%20neighbouring%20Telangana%20in%20November%20last%20year%2C%20may%20not%20be%20in%20the%20strongest%20bargaining%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20while%20a%20backroom%20deal%20seems%20more%20likely%2C%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20chances%20of%20winning%20that%20support%20is%20seen%20as%20lesser%20than%20that%20of%20his%20state%20rival.%20The%20BJP%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20has%20been%20giving%20him%20the%20cold%20shoulder%20because%20of%20the%20way%20he%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20party-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%2C%20twice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20was%20in%202018%2C%20when%20he%20was%20under%20pressure%20from%20Mr%20Reddy%20on%20the%20Special%20Category%20status%20issue.%20Back%20then%20the%20BJP%20had%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bdoors%20are%20closed%20forever%20(for%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20party)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20Mr%20Naidu%20has%20been%20on%20the%20backfoot%20with%20court%20cases%20filed%20against%20him%20and%20he%20will%2C%20therefore%2C%20prefer%20the%20party%20in%20power%20at%20the%20centre%20on%20his%20side.%20So%20he%20has%20been%20ma