or%20these%20sleeping%20bags%20came%20to%20him%20after%20experiencing%20the%20comfort%20of%20one%20during%20a%20camp%2C%20which%20helped%20him%20understand%20the%20practicality%20of%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20did%20he%20think%20of%20jeans%20to%20make%20sleeping%20bags%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDenim%20has%20very%20good%20insulation%20properties%2C%20and%20it%20is%20tough%20and%20lasts%20long.%20It%20is%20used%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20other%20countries%20to%20make%20insulation%20panels.%20On%20further%20research%2C%20I%20found%20that%20denim%20would%20be%20a%20much%20more%20rugged%20and%20long-term%20solution%20to%20battle%20the%20harsh%20winters.%20Blankets%20are%20not%20a%20complete%20and%20effective%20solution.%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20something%20that%20can%20be%20slept%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nirvaan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuoyed%20by%20the%20response%20to%20his%20pitch%20at%20the%20YA%2C%20the%20teenager%20decided%20to%20work%20on%20making%20his%20idea%20a%20reality.%20He%20had%20ready%20access%20to%20an%20expert%20at%20home%20%E2%80%94%20his%20mother%20Shivani%20who%20runs%20a%20clothing%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENirvaan%20pulled%20out%20his%20sleeping%20bag%2C%20opened%20it%20up%20and%20worked%20with%20his%20mother%20on%20how%20they%20could%20make%20a%20perfect%20one%20using%20old%20denim.%20They%20used%20the%20jeans%20they%20had%20at%20home%20and%20started%20experimenting%20with%20prototypes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20cutting%20the%20jeans%20in%20different%20sizes%20and%20lengths%20to%20understand%20what%20would%20work.%20We%20took%20help%20from%20our%20tailors%20to%20sew%20it.%20The%20first%20one%20was%20a%20little%20small.%20Every%20time%20we%20created%20a%20prototype%2C%20we%20compared%20it%20to%20the%20sleeping%20bag%20we%20had%20at%20home%20to%20achieve%20a%20similar%20level%20of%20comfort%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20his%20mother%2C%20Shivani%20Somany.%3