nia%20attack%20when%20he%20was%20three.%20Recalling%20that%20day%2C%20Moushmi%20remembers%20how%20she%20collapsed%20on%20the%20floor%20as%20she%20watched%20her%20toddler%20in%20the%20ICU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20didn%E2%80%99t%20tell%20me%20that%20they%20would%20put%20him%20on%20the%20ventilator.%20All%20I%20could%20see%20in%20the%20ICU%20was%20a%C2%A0%20pillow%20and%20my%20child%20on%20it.%20The%20pillow%20was%20bigger%20than%20him.%20Doctors%20had%20lost%20hope%20and%20told%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98Pray%20to%20God%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20tried%20our%20best%E2%80%99.%20It%20was%20all%20too%20much%20for%20me%20to%20take%20and%20I%20just%20collapsed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20remained%20on%20the%20ventilator%20for%20five%20days%2C%20an%20Indian%20doctor%20in%20the%20hospital%20advised%20the%20young%20couple%20to%20take%20the%20child%20to%20India%20for%20treatment.%20Moushmi%20shudders%20as%20she%20recalls%20the%20day%20they%20took%20their%20child%20off%20the%20ventilator%20to%20board%20the%20flight%20back%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20doctor%20there%20said%20that%20we%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20wean%20him%20off%20the%20ventilator%20if%20we%20stayed%20there.%20Medical%20facilities%20weren%E2%80%99t%20that%20good%20in%20Dubai%2020%20years%20back.%20A%20particular%20machine%2C%20which%20was%20required%20to%20help%20him%20breathe%2C%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20available.%20As%20soon%20as%20we%20arrived%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20we%20had%20three%20people%20ready%20with%20the%20instrument%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC1tMV1lA0I2%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC1tMV1lA0I2%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%