3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EL%26amp%3BT%20has%20undertaken%20a%20comprehensive%20approach%20to%20facilitate%20access%20to%20STEM%20education%20in%20government%20schools%20and%20schools%20with%20limited%20resources.%20This%20initiative%20is%20designed%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20and%20ensure%20that%20students%20have%20the%20necessary%20tools%20and%20opportunities%20to%20develop%20skills%20essential%20for%20the%20evolving%20job%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20different%20models%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20STEM%20education%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302015%2Fboson-whitewater-bengaluru-startup-converts-stp-water-to-high-quality-potable-drinking-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20science%20labs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20implementing%20digital%20classrooms%2C%20and%20providing%20DIY%20kits%2C%20among%20other%20approaches.%20We%20did%20not%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20just%20one%20model%2C%20and%20instead%2C%20we%20decided%20on%20a%20blended%20approach%2C%20working%20to%20address%20the%20specific%20needs%20of%20each%20school%20as%20cracking%20just%20one%20piece%20of%20the%20puzzle%20is%20not%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mabel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmbracing%20the%20Smart%20School%20concept%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20initially%20focussed%20on%20furnishing%20schools%20with%20fundamental%20infrastructure%20before%20progressing%20to%20the%20establishment%20of%20STEM%20labs.%20However%2C%20their%20original%20plan%20underwent%20adjustments%20due%20to%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20pandemic%20coinciding%20with%20the%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommencing%20with%2065%20schools%20nationwide%2C%20it%20pivoted%20to%20online%20classes%20and%20modules%20in%20response%20to%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20COVID-19.%20The%20volunteers%20distributed%20WhatsApp%20videos%20and%20assigned%20children%20straightforward%20DIY%20projects%20that%20could%20be%20completed%20using%20materials%20readily%20available%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Teachers%20note%20that%20these%20models%20not%20only%20let%20students%20display%20creativity%20but%20also%20assist%20in%20delivering%20more%20effective%20explanations%2C%20using%20the%20visual%20aids%20provided%20by%20the%20projects.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969-1536x864.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340838%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETeachers%20note%20that%20these%20models%20not%20only%20let%20students%20display%20creativity%20but%20also%20assist%20in%20delivering%20more%20effective%20explanations%2C%20using%20the%20visual%20aids%20provided%20by%20the%20projects.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChildren%20were%20excited%20to%20do%20the%20projects%20and%20they%20would%20share%20it%20eagerly.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20even%20hosted%20an%20online%20science%20fair%20to%20showcase%20their%20creations.%20We%20were%20amazed%20by%20the%20projects%20they%20came%20up%20with%3B%20it%20fired%20their%20creativity%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Mabel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EL%26amp%3BT%20collaborates%20with%20local%20NGO%20partners%20to%20implement%20the%20programme%20in%20selected%20schools%2C%20committing%20to%20support%20these%20schools%20for%20at%20least%20three%20to%20four%20years.%20The%20initiative%20works%20on%20dual%20fronts%20%E2%80%94%20providing%20training%20to%20teachers%20in%20STEM%20education%20and%20building%20physical%20infrastructure%20in%20schools%2C%20including%20STEM%20labs%20or%20digital%20classrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20begins%20with%20L%26amp%3BT%20selecting%20a%20school%2C%20and%20conducting%20an%20orientation%20and%20a%20needs%20assessment.%20A%20key%20criterion%20is%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20science%20teacher%2C%20and%20the%20initiative%20is%20tailored%20for%20students%20in%20Classes%206%20to%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20through%20NGO%20partners%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20delivers%20training%20to%20the%20district%20education%20officer%2C%20school%20principal%2C%20and%20teachers.%20Quarterly%20training%20sessions%20are%20conducted%20for%20teachers%2C%20with%20an%20observer%20present%20in%20the%20classroom%20to%20evaluate%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20teaching%20and%20provide%20guidance%20on%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20hands-on%20approach%20not%20only%20equips%20teachers%20to%20impart%20knowledge%20effectively%20but%20also%20strives%20to%20establish%20a%20sustainable%20model.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20empower%20teachers%20to%20continue%20delivering%20quality%20education%20independently%2C%20even%20without%20ongoing%20assistance%20from%20the%20NGO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20idea%20is%20to%20improve%20children%E2%80%99s%20conceptual%20understanding%20of%20science.%20Based%20on%20our%20observation%2C%20many%20students%20lose%20interest%20in%20science%20in%20Classes%206%20to%209.%20Girl%20students%20too%20face%20several%20biases%20and%20challenges%20as%20STEM%20courses%20are%20not%20traditionally%20considered%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20domain.%20If%20they%20get%20a%20better%